Time":"2017-08-25T05:56:50.000Z","msg":"我也是,但我已經收咗卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dff8ad5c6d064100bf7c7fdb229f5c4f6c6d0f8","tid":373451,"uid":59679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"沉船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n弱智就咪上連登啊"},{"pid":"f1f71dad8674fa6b6bf130bef91134d6a77bc668","tid":373451,"uid":49642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"OK, 唔屌樓主連沉船點解都唔撚知<br />\n<br />\n有冇其他女介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fd1de381fa7c0d85b9a7a6430b97b55013d4b2","tid":373451,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:24:13.000Z","msg":"我知邊個啦 係咪住大嶼山嗰邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa37da2b6975c5942eb000cd2cf767b88711f452","tid":373451,"uid":19214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:36:00.000Z","msg":"仲以為條女叫鴨叫到沉左船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}